
%h1 Copy Event Settings from another Tenant

%p
  This is a new feature which allows basic copying of events from a different Convention into the current convention.
  %br
  After copying the events, you should go through all the settings pages to ensure that all URLs, options, and references
  are still correct.

%h2 Migrate Events from: Choose Convention

%ul
  - @tenants.each do |tenant|
    %li= link_to tenant.subdomain, migrate_events_path(tenant: tenant.subdomain)
